Description: Linux driver and CUPS backend for the M08F A4 thermal printer
 Provides a CLI (m08f print/probe/calibrate/status) and a CUPS backend so the
 M08F A4 thermal printer (sold as Phomemo / COLORWING / AIMO) appears as a
 normal printer in any Linux application. Communicates over USB CDC/ACM in
 solid-red mode using the ESC/POS protocol.
